Product name: Crochet PATTERN No 1706 Alien by Krawka,
Description:
**Please note, this listing is for the PATTERN only, not the finished toy!**
Crochet alien, when finished, is 21 cm tall (8.2 inches). 
Alien franchise was one of the movies that made a huge impact on me when I was younger. I love the whole series, always had and always will, and as a huge fan I am so proud to present my newest creation - alien. After making he went straight to my private display and I am not giving him to anyone, anyone! :) I think he is scary with just a hint of cuteness in him which makes him so perfect, at least for me!
Although I am not giving my finished alien to anyone, anyone! I wrote the pattern and hope you will make a good use of it :) This pattern is for the medium advanced crocheters but if you are ready to try I am always ready to help. You should know basic crochet stitches including chain, slip stitch, single crochet, decrease, increase  and how to start with magic ring. 
I've put wires in his arms, legs and tail, but if you are doing this as a toy for a child (My little son loves monsters and aliens, but he is afraid of squirrels, true story:) I strongly recommend you to skip wiring, make a safe plush toy instead and sew everything twice as firmly as you would normally do (especially nails and teeth). 
If you would like to see the sample pattern you should visit my blog: krawka.blogspot.com where you will find many free crochet patterns.
For my projects I use yarn which meterage is 174 yards (159 meters) for 50 g, weight Sport / 5 ply (12 wpi), Gauge 24 to 30 st is 4 inches (10 cm) and 3 mm hook (if you can it's recommended to use 2 mm hook to make teeth and claws). If you want you can also prepare a wire.
If you would like to sign up for my newsletter with newest crochet patterns, discounts and much, much more click here: https://forms.aweber.com/form/78/1142518878.htm
Pattern will be available for download immediately after completing transaction.

Product name: Rose gold filled cuff, Rose gold bangle, Rose gold bracelet, 14k rose gold bangle, Slim rose gold cuff, Slim rose gold bangle, Made in UK
Description:
This lovely minimalist bracelet is made from 14k rose gold filled wire, the bangle is very simple in it's design using thin round 1.5mm wire that has been shaped and the ends have been hammered flat and then filed so that there are no sharp edges. The cuff is then tumbled to add a beautiful shine and added strength.
I can offer this bracelet in 3 sizes: Small - 6 inches, Medium - 7 inches and Large - 8 inches. As the ends are open it can be pulled apart or pushed together gently to ensure it is a perfect fit for you. To measure the hand, position it as though putting on a bangle, with the thumb tucked in against the palm. Wrap the measuring tape along the widest part of the hand. The measurement where the tape measure overlaps is the hand size.I can also make it to fit your upper arm - if you wish to order one please choose the  'upper arm' option on the size menu and add a note to me at checkout stating what size your bicep measures in either centimetres or inches.
Gold filled jewellery is a more affordable way to buy gold. The layer of 14k gold is far thicker than on plated items, it will last a lifetime if cared for and the gold layer will not rub off as many gold plated items will do eventually.
